XPath: /h4</note>
      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="10979" identifier="65f9ba25c7ba6c3df290f7c06de70769">
        <source>Can students reliably find the flipped card in a grid?
Can they articulate the algorithm to another student to help them complete the
task?</source>
        <target>crwdns10979:0crwdne10979:0</target>
        <note>Context: Paragraph text&#13;
XPath: /p[3]</note>
